{
  "stem": "8252.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would print that, write it out-- I don't remember, even-- and then take it to some of the forced labor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now that information contained, also, the information that Jews are being killed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, the extent of the-- of the Holocaust, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We knew that there are concentration camps where Jews are being killed, but we didn't-- nobody knew the cond-- the extent of it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was, I would say '42, '43.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And '44 beginning-- '44-- no, it was up till '44, up to January, '45 when, you know some-- in-- in this camp, anything of significance that happened that might be of interest is just-- the one Viennese guard who was-- who burst in one day with this happiness all over his face, the Americans are here.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was June 6, 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, and this man was so anti-Nazi that I couldn't exceed him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, he was in charge of the-- of the horse-- horse barn where our horses were, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a guard there, and I remember him coming in to-- you know, the on his face was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Americans are here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was this camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In this camp also, another story that happened once was that a truck got stuck in the mud, and I was with two friends-- Jews-- with me-- with me standing by.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the soldiers, the German soldiers who were driving the truck asked our help.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now French Jews-- and French altogether-- have a very special kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They do things, but they have to discuss them first for quite a long time, and talk about girls, and talk about food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, it takes time before they are ready to do anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, you know, they were talking.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
